headline.main: Lawyer for Vietnamese Woman in Kim's Death Wants 2nd Autopsy
headline.print_headline: Lawyer for Vietnamese Woman in Kim's Death Wants 2nd Autopsy

lead_paragraph: A lawyer for one of the women accused of poisoning the estranged half brother of North Korea's leader says there are serious holes in the case.
